{"TopicId":138600,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Stock Hovercraft (NEW Hovertank)","CreatedByName":"manni01","CreatedById":109903,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-30T23:23:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"manni01","CreatedById":109903,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-30T23:23:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022zTtKKRc.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022520\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/zTtKKRc.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:48px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003EStock Hovercraft\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022rQqFJAb.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/rQqFJAb.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I\u0027ve been playing around with wheels because are very different from the previous version of KSP. I found that rotation them in a specific way makes them have higher crash tolerance to an extend and lose all of\u00A0(if not 99.99% of)\u00A0the friction of the wheel. And the results seem pretty stable and reliable.\u00A0It can take quite the jumps, even on the mun. I might consider making different versions (like weaponized, sciencified, cargo-transport, etc.). There are two versions of this little 8 crew\u00A0craft. One made for Kerbin with jet engines:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzxHcRlvkLMQRVdlblV6N3V3bmM\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzxHcRlvkLMQRVdlblV6N3V3bmM\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the second version should work on all airless bodies (barring the ones that don\u0027t have decent gravity):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzxHcRlvkLMQYllYSktESy0tVE0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzxHcRlvkLMQYllYSktESy0tVE0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is the craft maneuvering as you\u0027d expect a hovercraft to work:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022CYzWjyS.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/CYzWjyS.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt even works on weird terrain (and water):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022XSTGJEa.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/XSTGJEa.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do want to note that since there is no friction on the wheels anymore, the craft can just glide sideways:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dAaaP2I.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/dAaaP2I.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I would like to point out the the CoT and CoM aren\u0027t aligned, which may cause some issues on the Mun if you are using full thrust a lot. It shouldn\u0027t be noticeable on kerbin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022jHkFN2V.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/jHkFN2V.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTell any problems you are experiencing any \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, I said I was gonna do more, and so I have (And I\u0027ll do even more)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve created a hovertank. It uses the same hovertank technology but, it also has turrent bearing (this tank version is only for looks, but don\u0027t worry, I\u0027m making one with plentiful weapons)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022W3NX8Fr.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/W3NX8Fr.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022TESQOFv.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/TESQOFv.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022GdBmEbT.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/GdBmEbT.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzxHcRlvkLMQckxyTUttRTAySzA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzxHcRlvkLMQckxyTUttRTAySzA\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-04T23:00:11Z\u0022 title=\u002205/04/2016 11:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by manni01\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded Hovertank\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mrmcp1","CreatedById":79657,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-01T10:34:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts nice to see someone else using this method. It looks really good.\u00A0How stable is yours?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOften when going over jumps mine looses a wheel. (it has about 30 of them so it has lots of redundancy)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/nCzZuF4.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022nCzZuF4.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"manni01","CreatedById":109903,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-04T23:00:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdded new hovertank\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022W3NX8Fr.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/W3NX8Fr.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022TESQOFv.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/TESQOFv.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022GdBmEbT.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/GdBmEbT.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzxHcRlvkLMQckxyTUttRTAySzA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://drive.google.com/open?id=0BzxHcRlvkLMQckxyTUttRTAySzA\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}